    <item>
      <title>对 SRT 信用风险的担忧日益加剧</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-16/concerns-about-credit-risk-in-srts-are-growing-credit-weekly</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在监管机构警告重大风险转移（一种银行资本减免）可能对金融稳定构成风险的背景下，市场参与者越来越担心此类转移带来的信用风险。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-16/concerns-about-credit-risk-in-srts-are-growing-credit-weekly</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 16 Nov 2024 20:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登总统最后进入亚太经合组织家庭照</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-11-16/president-joe-biden-enters-last-for-apec-family-photo-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[世界各国领导人在秘鲁利马举行的亚太经合组织会议期间合影留念。拜登总统最后到达合影现场，然后站在泰国和越南领导人之间，按照预先确定的立场站位。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-11-16/president-joe-biden-enters-last-for-apec-family-photo-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 16 Nov 2024 19:55:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登考虑限制化石燃料融资，其持续时间可能比特朗普任期更长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-16/biden-mulls-fossil-fuel-finance-curbs-that-could-outlast-trump</link>
      <description><![CDATA[拜登政府正在考虑在巴黎关键谈判开始之前尽最后一搏，争取达成一项国际协议，限制对外国石油和天然气项目的资金支持。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-16/biden-mulls-fossil-fuel-finance-curbs-that-could-outlast-trump</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 16 Nov 2024 18:34:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马斯克在财政部竞选中支持卢特尼克，反对贝森特</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-16/musk-throws-support-to-lutnick-over-bessent-in-treasury-race</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在各大阵营为争夺这一令人垂涎的内阁职位做最后努力之际，亿万富翁埃隆·马斯克表示支持霍华德·卢特尼克竞选总统当选人唐纳德·特朗普的下一任财政部长。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-16/musk-throws-support-to-lutnick-over-bessent-in-treasury-race</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 16 Nov 2024 17:27:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>MicroStrategy 的 260 亿美元比特币储备比 IBM、Nike 的现金储备还要多</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-16/microstrategy-s-26-billion-bitcoin-cache-is-larger-than-ibm-nike-cash-holdings</link>
      <description><![CDATA[迈克尔·塞勒 (Michael Saylor) 做出了一个非常规决定，在微策略公司 (MicroStrategy Inc.) 的账簿上持有比特币而不是现金，这使得这家曾经默默无闻的软件制造商在金融资产方面一跃成为最富有的公司之一。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-16/microstrategy-s-26-billion-bitcoin-cache-is-larger-than-ibm-nike-cash-holdings</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 16 Nov 2024 16:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>习近平宣布中国将于2026年主办亚太经合组织峰会</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-16/china-will-host-apec-summit-in-2026-xi-jinping-announces</link>
      <description><![CDATA[国家主席习近平宣布，中国将于2026年主办亚太经合组织峰会，峰会将汇聚21个成员国领导人——包括可能的美国当选总统唐纳德·特朗普——以及世界第二大经济体。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-16/china-will-host-apec-summit-in-2026-xi-jinping-announces</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 16 Nov 2024 15:57:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>COP29 冲突不断，沙特拒绝重申化石燃料承诺</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-16/cop29-clash-brews-as-saudis-resist-restating-fossil-fuel-pledge</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在联合国气候会谈中，各国是否应该重新履行去年做出的摆脱化石燃料的历史性承诺的争论愈演愈烈。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-16/cop29-clash-brews-as-saudis-resist-restating-fossil-fuel-pledge</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 16 Nov 2024 14:33:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>尽管OMV断供，俄罗斯仍继续向欧洲输送天然气</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-16/russian-gas-flows-are-steady-even-after-gazprom-cut-off-omv</link>
      <description><![CDATA[即使在切断与其最长期的合作伙伴之一奥地利 OMV AG 的联系后，俄罗斯天然气工业股份公司 (Gazprom PJSC) 仍以正常水平通过乌克兰向欧洲输送天然气。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-16/russian-gas-flows-are-steady-even-after-gazprom-cut-off-omv</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 16 Nov 2024 09:16:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>习近平担任全球自由贸易捍卫者，对抗特朗普</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-16/xi-seizes-role-as-global-defender-of-free-trade-against-trump</link>
      <description><![CDATA[当唐纳德·特朗普威胁对全世界征收关税时，习近平再次毫不犹豫地将自己定位为国际贸易体系的首要捍卫者。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-16/xi-seizes-role-as-global-defender-of-free-trade-against-trump</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 16 Nov 2024 00:23:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
